NORTHERN ZONE   

Northern Group

First Phase

[Aug 7 and 14]
Sampaio Corrêa  3-0   0-2  River
[Aug 16] - playoff   
River           2-1  Sampaio Corrêa

Semifinal

[Sep 1 and 7]
River           1-3   0-1  Paysandu

Final

[Sep 15 and 19]
Paysandu        0-1   0-2  Sport

Northeastern Group

First Phase

[Jul 21 and 28]
Campinense      2-2   0-0  ABC
